1: Don't create thumbnail (thumb.db) files for network drives.

See also
  HKCU/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion/Explorer/Advanced/DisableThumbnailCache
(https://github.com/ReneNyffenegger/about-Windows-Registry/blob/master/HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion/Explorer/Advanced/DisableThumbnailCache)

